OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry start
OL,6,Fto the evening, but turning
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy with patchy rain
OL,8,Fexpected to spread across from the
OL,9,Fwest during the rest of the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FCloudy with a few spots of
OL,12,Flight rain, but some brighter spells
OL,13,Fdeveloping in the afternoon. Outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain will then spread northeast
OL,15,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
